Continue from the previous zDash implementation.

Project:

⬡ zDash · FULL SYSTEM BLUEPRINT v2.0

Now execute ONLY:

PHASE 11 · AI OPS + GOVERNANCE + COMPLIANCE CONTROL PLANE
Model Governance + Prompt Registry + Evaluation System + Policy Engine + Security Review + Marketplace Review Pipeline

Do not rebuild Phase 1–10 from scratch.
Extend the existing codebase cleanly.

Assume these phases already exist:

