============================================================
CONFIG REQUIREMENTS
============================================================

Update root `.env.example`:

AIOPS_ENABLED=true
AIOPS_TRACE_ENABLED=true
AIOPS_COST_TRACKING_ENABLED=true
AIOPS_PROVIDER_ROUTING_ENABLED=true
AIOPS_DEFAULT_PROVIDER=mock
AIOPS_FAIL_CLOSED=true

PROMPT_REGISTRY_ENABLED=true
PROMPT_APPROVAL_REQUIRED=true
PROMPT_DEFAULT_STATUS=draft
PROMPT_RENDER_MAX_LENGTH=12000

EVALS_ENABLED=true
EVALS_MAX_CASES_PER_RUN=100
EVALS_STORE_RESULTS=true
EVALS_DEFAULT_DATASET=mock

REDTEAM_ENABLED=true
REDTEAM_DRY_RUN=true
REDTEAM_MAX_CASES_PER_RUN=50

GOVERNANCE_ENABLED=true
POLICY_ENGINE_ENABLED=true
POLICY_FAIL_CLOSED=true
APPROVAL_WORKFLOW_ENABLED=true

DLP_ENABLED=true
DLP_BLOCK_SECRETS=true
DLP_BLOCK_PRIVATE_KEYS=true
DLP_BLOCK_TOKENS=true
DLP_WARN_EMAILS=true

RETENTION_ENABLED=true
RETENTION_DEFAULT_DAYS=90
RETENTION_AUDIT_LOG_DAYS=365
RETENTION_AI_TRACE_DAYS=30
RETENTION_EVAL_RESULT_DAYS=180

COMPLIANCE_ENABLED=true
COMPLIANCE_EVIDENCE_ENABLED=true
COMPLIANCE_REPORTS_ENABLED=true
COMPLIANCE_EXPORT_REQUIRES_ADMIN=true

PLUGIN_REVIEW_REQUIRED=true
PLUGIN_SECURITY_SCAN_REQUIRED=true
PLUGIN_APPROVAL_REQUIRED=true

Rules:
- Missing config must fail safely.
- Production must fail closed when governance is enabled.
- Prompt approval is required by default.
- Plugin approval is required by default.
- AI traces must redact secrets.
- Compliance exports must exclude secrets by default.
- Red-team mode must be dry-run and defensive by default.

