Endpoints:

GET /api/governance/status

Policies:
GET /api/governance/policies
POST /api/governance/policies
PATCH /api/governance/policies/{policy_id}
POST /api/governance/evaluate

Approval:
GET /api/governance/approvals
POST /api/governance/approvals
POST /api/governance/approvals/{request_id}/approve
POST /api/governance/approvals/{request_id}/reject
POST /api/governance/approvals/{request_id}/cancel

DLP:
POST /api/governance/dlp/scan-text
POST /api/governance/dlp/scan-json

Retention:
GET /api/governance/retention/policies
POST /api/governance/retention/policies
POST /api/governance/retention/apply

Security review:
POST /api/governance/security-review
GET /api/governance/security-review/{review_id}

Rules:
- Auth required.
- Tenant scoped.
- Admin/operator manage policies.
- Analyst may run read-only DLP scan.
- Retention apply requires admin.
- All decisions audited.

