============================================================
API RESPONSE FORMAT
============================================================

All endpoints must use standard response shape:

Success:

{
  "ok": true,
  "data": {},
  "error": null,
  "timestamp": "ISO_DATE"
}

Error:

{
  "ok": false,
  "data": null,
  "error": {
    "code": "ERROR_CODE",
    "message": "Human readable message"
  },
  "timestamp": "ISO_DATE"
}

Required error codes:

- AIOPS_DISABLED
- MODEL_NOT_FOUND
- MODEL_DISABLED
- PROMPT_NOT_FOUND
- PROMPT_NOT_APPROVED
- PROMPT_DLP_BLOCKED
- EVAL_RUN_FAILED
- REDTEAM_BLOCKED
- POLICY_BLOCKED
- APPROVAL_REQUIRED
- APPROVAL_NOT_FOUND
- DLP_SCAN_FAILED
- DLP_SECRET_DETECTED
- RETENTION_NOT_ALLOWED
- COMPLIANCE_EXPORT_BLOCKED
- SECURITY_REVIEW_FAILED
- TENANT_ACCESS_DENIED

